{"tid":1691223,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再on 99係曱甴屋外淨係叫口號啦，對家少少傷都冇","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T14:54:02.000Z","uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6958f06119608ffe7781174cd7a6baadb8998f","tid":1691223,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"反正大家都係冇膽衝冇膽打，班狗一落車又嚇到跑幾條街，叫幾句解散警隊有咩用呀<br />\n <br />\n人地當我地傻西炸<br />\n<br />\n我有提議， 反正都係叫，不如搵人帶個喇叭，唔好淨係叫口號，而係將老豆搵仔上面既曱甴狗及其家屬的資料讀出黎，有記者直播更好，等全世界人都知道，咁先至有威脅架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係望過下，老豆搵仔d 資料係冇所屬曱甴屋呢欄，一係大家以住址去區別<br />\n<br />\n所以希望老豆搵仔集埋班仆街的所屬曱甴屋或隊伍，方便有手足分類再大聲揚開去"},{"pid":"6649bbdf6e3c8752c581227c1bb85717cdb9fcbc","tid":1691223,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"曱近平1"},{"pid":"070bcf2608840afddbfb02c48c220c522014fa63","tid":1691223,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"曱近平2"},{"pid":"4dc2a07792911a663a77bffee072ae48b679c420","tid":1691223,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"曱近平3"},{"pid":"47c9ff658450f50cf48b510c4daf21ae5b731c92","tid":1691223,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:43:17.000Z","msg":"曱近平4"},{"pid":"2ceb2c4f219a0754d840a52d9e61b21b6c61629c","tid":1691223,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"曱近平5"},{"pid":"cfd7292c6520f5130fbf544ff147f3f24185b40f","tid":1691223,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"曱近平6"},{"pid":"b246300bf725fca5b6ccb5e66740496d66731956","tid":1691223,"uid":266508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019